lemma inv_2 : "(\<tau> \<Turnstile> Person .allInstances@pre()->includes\<^sub>S\<^sub>e\<^sub>t(self)) \<Longrightarrow> (\<tau> \<Turnstile> inv\<^sub>P\<^sub>e\<^sub>r\<^sub>s\<^sub>o\<^sub>n\<^sub>_\<^sub>l\<^sub>a\<^sub>b\<^sub>e\<^sub>l\<^sub>A\<^sub>T\<^sub>p\<^sub>r\<^sub>e(self)) = ((\<tau> \<Turnstile> (self .boss@pre \<doteq> null)) \<or> (\<tau> \<Turnstile> (self .boss@pre <> null) \<and> (\<tau> \<Turnstile> (self .boss@pre .salary@pre \<le>\<^sub>i\<^sub>n\<^sub>t self .salary@pre)) \<and> (\<tau> \<Turnstile> (inv\<^sub>P\<^sub>e\<^sub>r\<^sub>s\<^sub>o\<^sub>n\<^sub>_\<^sub>l\<^sub>a\<^sub>b\<^sub>e\<^sub>l\<^sub>A\<^sub>T\<^sub>p\<^sub>r\<^sub>e(self .boss@pre)))))"
